<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>Aryadhar Gupta — Driver, Builder & Engineering Creator</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Aryadhar Gupta is a motorsport driver, builder, engineering creator, CAD user, IoT maker, and climate activist based in Delhi, India."
    />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#f6f4ef" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f6f4ef;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --surface-soft: #f0ede6;
        --text: #171717;
        --muted: #5f6268;
        --subtle: #8a8d93;
        --line: #dedbd3;
        --accent: #12355b;
        --accent-soft: #e8eef5;
        --max: 1120px;
        --radius: 18px;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
      }

      img,
      video {
        max-width: 100%;
        display: block;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
      }

      p,
      h1,
      h2,
      h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .wrap {
        width: min(calc(100% - 32px), var(--max));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .site-header {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 20;
        background: rgba(246, 244, 239, 0.92);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .nav {
        min-height: 72px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .brand {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .brand-mark {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--text);
        color: var(--bg);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        gap: 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.93rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .nav-cta {
        color: var(--accent) !important;
        font-weight: 650;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 96px 0 72px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(280px, 0.6fr);
        gap: 56px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 780px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.8rem);
        line-height: 0.98;
        letter-spacing: -0.07em;
      }

      .lead {
        max-width: 680px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 32px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        min-height: 44px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border: 1px solid var(--text);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 650;
        transition:
          background 180ms ease,
          color 180ms ease,
          border-color 180ms ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: var(--text);
        color: var(--bg);
      }

      .button.primary {
        background: var(--text);
        color: var(--bg);
      }

      .button.primary:hover {
        background: var(--accent);
        border-color: var(--accent);
      }

      .profile-card {
        padding: 24px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        background: var(--surface);
      }

      .profile-card h2 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .profile-card p {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .profile-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0;
        margin-top: 22px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .profile-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
        gap: 14px;
        padding: 13px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        font-size: 0.93rem;
      }

      .profile-row span:first-child {
        color: var(--subtle);
      }

      .profile-row span:last-child {
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .proof {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 170px), 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 44px;
      }

      .proof-item {
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
      }

      .proof-item strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .proof-item span {
        display: block;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.45;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 78px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .section-head {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(280px, 0.55fr);
        gap: 36px;
        align-items: end;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .kicker {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 750;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 680px;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
        line-height: 1.02;
        letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      }

      .section-note {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .two-col {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 0.75fr);
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 26px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        background: var(--surface);
      }

      .card p {
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .card p + p {
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .quote {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        min-height: 100%;
        background: var(--text);
        color: var(--bg);
      }

      .quote p {
        color: rgba(246, 244, 239, 0.74);
      }

      blockquote {
        margin: 0 0 22px;
        font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.4vw, 1.9rem);
        line-height: 1.18;
        letter-spacing: -0.045em;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .tag-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 28px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--surface-soft);
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .quote .tag {
        border-color: rgba(246, 244, 239, 0.24);
        background: rgba(246, 244, 239, 0.08);
        color: rgba(246, 244, 239, 0.82);
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 245px), 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .capability-card {
        min-height: 245px;
      }

      .number {
        margin-bottom: 34px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 750;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.12rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      }

      .project-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        min-height: 330px;
      }

      .project-type {
        margin-bottom: 36px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 750;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .project-card .tag-row {
        margin-top: auto;
        padding-top: 24px;
      }

      .project-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .text-link {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
      }

      .timeline {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .timeline-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
        gap: 26px;
        padding: 22px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .timeline-card:last-child {
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .year {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 750;
      }

      .timeline-card h3 {
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      .timeline-card p {
        max-width: 760px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .press-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 320px), 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .press-links {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .media-placeholder {
        min-height: 240px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 1px dashed #c9c5ba;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .media-placeholder strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-size: 1.12rem;
      }

      .media-placeholder span {
        display: block;
        max-width: 560px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .contact {
        border-bottom: 0;
      }

      .contact-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.8fr) minmax(280px, 1fr);
        gap: 28px;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        background: var(--surface);
      }

      .contact-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 210px), 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .contact-item {
        padding: 15px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: var(--bg);
      }

      .contact-item span {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        color: var(--subtle);
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        font-weight: 750;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .contact-item a,
      .contact-item strong {
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 650;
        text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 28px 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .footer-inner {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero-grid,
        .section-head,
        .two-col,
        .contact-card {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 72px 0 56px;
        }

        .section {
          padding: 62px 0;
        }

        .nav {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
          padding: 14px 0;
        }

        .nav-links {
          justify-content: flex-start;
          gap: 14px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 560px) {
        .wrap {
          width: min(calc(100% - 24px), var(--max));
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: clamp(2.55rem, 14vw, 3.8rem);
          letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        }

        .profile-row,
        .timeline-card {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 4px;
        }

        .card,
        .profile-card,
        .contact-card {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero-actions {
          align-items: stretch;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .button {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="wrap nav">
        <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="Aryadhar Gupta homepage">
          <span class="brand-mark">AG</span>
          <span>Aryadhar Gupta</span>
        </a>

        <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary navigation">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#capabilities">Capabilities</a>
          <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
          <a href="#timeline">Timeline</a>
          <a href="#press">Press</a>
          <a class="nav-cta" href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="top">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="hero-grid">
            <div>
              <div class="eyebrow">Driver • Builder • Creator</div>

              <h1>Engineering discipline, built through machines.</h1>

              <p class="lead">
                I work across motorsport, mechanical systems, CAD, connected
                hardware, and climate-focused leadership — combining track
                experience with practical, hands-on technical execution.
              </p>

              <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="button primary" href="#projects">View Projects</a>
                <a class="button" href="#contact">Start a Conversation</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <aside class="profile-card">
              <h2>Professional focus</h2>
              <p>
                Building a serious technical and motorsport profile for racing
                opportunities, sponsorship conversations, engineering projects,
                and selected collaborations.
              </p>

              <div class="profile-list">
                <div class="profile-row">
                  <span>Base</span>
                  <span>Delhi, India</span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-row">
                  <span>Areas</span>
                  <span>Motorsport, CAD, IoT, automotive systems</span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-row">
                  <span>Style</span>
                  <span>Hands-on, fast-learning, execution-focused</span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-row">
                  <span>Open to</span>
                  <span>Teams, sponsors, technical collaborations</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>

          <div class="proof" aria-label="Key credibility markers">
            <div class="proof-item">
              <strong>Formula-4 Testing</strong>
              <span>Driver development and circuit experience.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="proof-item">
              <strong>Drift Instructor</strong>
              <span>BAD BOI DRIFTS, car control and coaching.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="proof-item">
              <strong>UNO Minda</strong>
              <span>Product Integration & Market Analysis.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="proof-item">
              <strong>2nd at BIC</strong>
              <span>Autocross result at Buddh International Circuit.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="proof-item">
              <strong>CAD Since 2016</strong>
              <span>Design, prototyping, fixtures and mechanisms.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="proof-item">
              <strong>Mensa Member</strong>
              <span>Analytical problem-solving and fast learning.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="kicker">About</div>
              <h2 class="section-title">A builder’s mindset, shaped by real systems.</h2>
            </div>

            <p class="section-note">
              A focused overview for teams, sponsors, collaborators, and anyone
              evaluating the work behind the name.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="two-col">
            <article class="card">
              <p>
                My work started with physical curiosity: dismantling, repairing,
                testing, and building RC models, cars, boats, planes, drones,
                and mechanical systems. That foundation grew into CAD design,
                aeromodelling, coding, IoT systems, automotive restoration, and
                motorsport.
              </p>

              <p>
                Today, I combine driving experience with technical depth:
                Formula-4 testing, drift instruction, autocross competition,
                product-facing industry exposure, and self-built hardware
                projects. The common standard across all of it is simple:
                understand the system properly, then improve it.
              </p>

              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">Motorsport</span>
                <span class="tag">Mechanical Systems</span>
                <span class="tag">CAD</span>
                <span class="tag">IoT</span>
                <span class="tag">Automotive</span>
                <span class="tag">Climate Advocacy</span>
              </div>
            </article>

            <aside class="card quote">
              <blockquote>
                The goal is not to look technical. The goal is to build, test,
                refine, and make the machine better.
              </blockquote>

              <p>
                This portfolio will grow into a complete record of projects,
                media, case studies, racing experience, and technical work.
              </p>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="capabilities" class="section">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="kicker">Capabilities</div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Where I create value.</h2>
            </div>

            <p class="section-note">
              Four connected areas define the profile: driving, mechanics,
              design, and connected systems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid">
            <article class="card capability-card">
              <div class="number">01</div>
              <h3>Motorsport & Driver Development</h3>
              <p>
                Formula-4 testing, drift instruction, autocross competition,
                simulator work, car control, video review, and performance
                iteration.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="card capability-card">
              <div class="number">02</div>
              <h3>Mechanical & Automotive Work</h3>
              <p>
                Hands-on diagnostics, restoration planning, powertrain
                understanding, workshop problem-solving, and real mechanical
                execution.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="card capability-card">
              <div class="number">03</div>
              <h3>CAD, Prototyping & Fabrication</h3>
              <p>
                CAD-led development for functional parts, assemblies, brackets,
                housings, airframes, fixtures, and prototype mechanisms.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="card capability-card">
              <div class="number">04</div>
              <h3>Software, IoT & Control Systems</h3>
              <p>
                Web interfaces, ESP8266/Arduino projects, automation logic,
                embedded control, and systems that connect software to hardware.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="projects" class="section">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="kicker">Selected Work</div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Projects that demonstrate execution.</h2>
            </div>

            <p class="section-note">
              Media and case studies will be added later. For now, the structure
              stays clean, professional, and text-first.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid">
            <article class="card project-card">
              <div class="project-type">Connected Hardware</div>

              <h3>NodeMCU Traffic Light Controller</h3>

              <p>
                ESP8266-controlled traffic light system using AC relays, web UI
                controls, persistent timing logic, and planned Wi-Fi based
                audio-reactive behavior.
              </p>

              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">ESP8266</span>
                <span class="tag">Web UI</span>
                <span class="tag">Relays</span>
                <span class="tag">IoT</span>
              </div>

             <div class="project-links">
  <a class="text-link" href="/traffic-control/">
    Control My Lights
  </a>

  <a
    class="text-link"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener"
    href="https://aryadharg-max.github.io/traffic-light-control/"
  >
    Live demo
  </a>

  <a
    class="text-link"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener"
    href="https://github.com/aryadharg-max/traffic-light-control"
  >
    GitHub
  </a>
</div>
            </article>

            <article class="card project-card">
              <div class="project-type">Automotive</div>

              <h3>Lexus GS300 / 2JZ Work</h3>

              <p>
                Hands-on automotive project work focused on mechanical
                reliability, diagnosis, restoration planning, and clean
                execution around the 2JZ platform.
              </p>

              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">2JZ</span>
                <span class="tag">Diagnostics</span>
                <span class="tag">Restoration</span>
                <span class="tag">Mechanical</span>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="card project-card">
              <div class="project-type">Aero + RC</div>

              <h3>Aeromodelling & RC Prototyping</h3>

              <p>
                RC aircraft and vehicle builds involving airframe design, weight
                balance, powertrain integration, control surfaces, and iterative
                testing.
              </p>

              <div class="tag-row">
                <span class="tag">RC</span>
                <span class="tag">Airframes</span>
                <span class="tag">Powertrain</span>
                <span class="tag">Testing</span>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="timeline" class="section">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <div class="kicker">Timeline</div>
              <h2 class="section-title">Development path.</h2>
            </div>

            <p class="section-note">
              A simplified timeline of how the interests became a usable
              professional profile.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline">
            <article class="timeline-card">
              <div class="year">2013+</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Early engineering curiosity</h3>
                <p>
                  Built the foundation through dismantling, repairing,
                  experimenting, RC models, workshop tinkering, and mechanical
                  curiosity.
                </p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="timeline-card">
              <div class="year">2016</div>
              <div>
                <h3>CAD and design proficiency</h3>
